 in Khasimara ghat; they have have been surviving on relief after their homes were destroyed by Cyclone Yaas <img alt=\"\" class=\"lazyload\" data-src=\"\" src=\"/media/images/08-13_Abhijit-AC.width-1440.jpg\" style=\" height:auto;\"/> PHOTO \u2022 Abhijit Chakraborty Food grains and rations arriving by boat at the Khasimara ghat <img alt=\"\" class=\"lazyload\" data-src=\"\" src=\"/media/images/09-14_Abhijit-AC.width-1440.jpg\" style=\" height:auto;\"/> PHOTO \u2022 Abhijit Chakraborty Men, women, children and cattle getting off the ferry, all in a hurry to return home <img alt=\"\" class=\"lazyload\" data-src=\"\" src=\"/media/images/10-09_Abhijit-AC.width-1440.jpg\" style=\" height:auto;\"/> PHOTO \u2022 Abhijit Chakraborty Temporary shelter in Tank Ground near Mandirtala bajar , Ghoramara's highest point. Nearly a third of the villagers sought shelter here <img alt=\"\" class=\"lazyload\" data-src=\"\" src=\"/media/images/11-16_Abhijit-AC.width-1440.jpg\" style=\" height:auto;\"/> PHOTO \u2022 Abhijit Chakraborty Amit Haldar standing near his damaged house.", "start_char_idx": null, "end_char_idx": null, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_seperator": "\n"}, "__type__": "1"}, "c19fc712-1583-4353-a085-60074dbf0faa": {"__data__": {"id_": "c19fc712-1583-4353-a085-60074dbf0faa", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://ruralindiaonline.org/en/articles/i-have-to-leave-ghoramara-but-why-should-i/", "Author": "\n\n\n\n\nAbhijit Chakraborty\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n", "Publisher": "People's Archive of Rural India", "Type": "Web"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "\u2018I have to leave Ghoramara, but why should I?\u2019", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://ruralindiaonline.org/en/articles/i-have-to-leave-ghoramara-but-why-should-i/", "Author": "\n\n\n\n\nAbhijit Chakraborty\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n", "Publisher": "People's